thread.title: maria

author: maria
title: maria
text: ordered 2 dashmats after the advice from the chat. One fitted and one didn't. When I got in touch, their response was quick. I purchased another one they recommended and when it arrived sent the other one back. (at my expense). I received my refund quickly. Had I thought about it a bit more, I could have got $10 off my second purchase which would have cut down on the cost of postage.
